  <sect3 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of Aisleriot</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Aisleriot</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --sysconfdir=/etc \
            --disable-static \
            --with-card-theme-formats=svg \
            --libexecdir=/usr/lib &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect3>

  <sect3 role="commands">
    <title>Command Explanations</title>

    <para>
      <parameter>--with-card-theme-formats=svg</parameter> Specifies
      which theme format to use. Available options are:
      svg,fixed,kde,pysol.
    </para>

    <para>
      <parameter>--disable-static</parameter>: Prevents the static
      libraries being built and installed.
    </para>

    <para>
      <option>--enable-sound</option>: Enables
      <application>libcanberra</application>
      sound.
    </para>

  </sect3>

